column2: SELECT top # distinct G.objID,mn.ldist_z,G.u,G.g,G.r,G.i,G.z,a.h_alpha_flux,a.h_alpha_eqw, emline.sigmaStars as emline_vdisp FROM Galaxy as G join GalSpecLine as a on G.SpecobjID = a.SpecObjID  join stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS pca ON G.specobjid = pca.specobjid  join emissionLinesPort as emline on pca.specobjid = emline.specobjid  JOIN specObj as sp ON emline.specobjid = sp.specobjid JOIN mangaDAPall as mn on G.htmID = mn.htmID
